HEADWORD: Polyclinic
<hw>Pol`y*clin"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets> + <ets>clinic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A clinic in which diseases of many sorts are treated; especially,
an institution in which clinical instruction is given in all kinds of
disease.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

